	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, when I worked at a chemical plant, I've blended some nasty mixtures used for this purpose.  With stuff like methylene chloride and glacial acetic acid, don't even think about using that stuff without full respiratory, face, and skin protection.  It's like vinegar from hell.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
